                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/wangchenzi1/">小护士毒舌猫-虞兮虞兮奈若何</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2015-11-11</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">感觉不用再读老先生的书了，连看了三本他想说啥都明白了。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
